===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[sword]]-like [[tool]] used for [[cut]]ting large [[plant]]s with a [[chop]]ping motion.  A machete's blade is usually 50 to 65 centimeters ([[cm]]) long, and up to three millimeters ([[mm]]) thick.

